## Name: short name, decoupled from OS hostname
-sname erlkoenig

## Cookie: DEVELOPMENT ONLY — deploy generates a random cookie.
## NEVER use this in production. See SECURITY.md.
-setcookie erlkoenig_dev

## Scheduler busy-wait threshold
+sbwt very_short

## Distribution: bind to localhost, pin port range
-kernel inet_dist_listen_min 9100
-kernel inet_dist_listen_max 9155
-kernel inet_dist_use_interface '{127,0,0,1}'
